msgid "Event listener order <span id=\"event-listener-order\"></span>"
msgstr "Gestores de Eventos <span id=\"event-handlers\"></span>"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/concept/events.md
msgid "When several listeners are configured for the same event, they are called in the order they are listed in the config.  If an event implements `Psr\\EventDispatcher\\StoppableEventInterface`, the dispatcher checks `isPropagationStopped()` before calling the next listener. When it returns `true`, the dispatcher stops processing the event."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/concept/events.md
msgid "Keep listeners independent where possible. Ordering is useful for technical needs, but business logic is usually easier to maintain when each listener can run on its own."
msgstr ""

